{"tid":2368063,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"華為5G技術與SpaceX公司的星鏈技術比，不堪一擊？","createTime":"2021-01-16T00:36:33.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-19T06:45:43.000Z","uid":25345,"like":28,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":43,"replies":[{"pid":"9bf792e4ad18fd2661036a403c9667b241da3f82","tid":2368063,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T00:36:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://nimg.ws.126.net/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fdingyue.ws.126.net%2F2021%2F0113%2F7a95c024j00qmvm4e000wc000hs00aom.jpg&amp;thumbnail=650x2147483647&amp;quality=80&amp;type=jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnimg.ws.126.net%2F%3Furl%3Dhttp%253A%252F%252Fdingyue.ws.126.net%252F2021%252F0113%252F7a95c024j00qmvm4e000wc000hs00aom.jpg%26thumbnail%3D650x2147483647%26quality%3D80%26type%3Djpg&h=dbcff470&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n  2015年1月，馬斯克宣布SpaceX計劃將約1.2萬顆通信衛星發射到軌道，其中1584顆將部署在地球上空550千米處的近地軌道，並從2020年開始工作。這一項目被命名為&ldquo;星鏈&rdquo;（Starlink）。但據有關文件顯示，該公司還準備再增加3萬顆，使衛星總量達到約4.2萬顆。<br />\n<br />\n  <br />\n<br />\n  每顆225Kg一輛汽車大小。星鏈計劃有望覆蓋地球上所有難以涉足地方。<br />\n<br />\n  4月23日，SpaceX成功發射第七批60顆Starlink衛星，馬斯克發推特說，星鏈內測差不多三個月後開始，公測六個月以後。<br />\n<br />\n  <img src=\"https://nimg.ws.126.net/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fdingyue.ws.126.net%2F2021%2F0113%2Fae664129j00qmvm4e000rc000hs00a0m.jpg&amp;thumbnail=650x2147483647&amp;quality=80&amp;type=jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnimg.ws.126.net%2F%3Furl%3Dhttp%253A%252F%252Fdingyue.ws.126.net%252F2021%252F0113%252Fae664129j00qmvm4e000rc000hs00a0m.jpg%26thumbnail%3D650x2147483647%26quality%3D80%26type%3Djpg&h=de016cf9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n  馬斯克補充說，最初的測試將適用於高緯度地區。星鏈服務最初將在2020年提供給加拿大和北美客戶，並在2021年進一步擴大服務範圍至世界其他地區。<br />\n<br />\n  其實這種衛星電話並不是馬斯克首創，當年摩托羅拉投資的銥星系統就這麼幹過，但錢燒沒了，最終也掛了，而SpaceX沒蹈銥星的覆轍，原因就在於其較成熟的火箭回收技術。而其競爭對手OneWeb疫情期間軟銀撤資而宣布破產，與此同時SpaceX卻新獲5億美金融資，說明成本因素是SpaceX仍舊受資本市場追捧的原因之一。<br />\n<br />\n  <img src=\"https://nimg.ws.126.net/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fdingyue.ws.126.net%2F2021%2F0113%2Ff86724b2j00qmvm4e000lc000du007gm.jpg&amp;thumbnail=650x2147483647&amp;quality=80&amp;type=jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnimg.ws.126.net%2F%3Furl%3Dhttp%253A%252F%252Fdingyue.ws.126.net%252F2021%252F0113%252Ff86724b2j00qmvm4e000lc000du007gm.jpg%26thumbnail%3D650x2147483647%26quality%3D80%26type%3Djpg&h=6520c839&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n  福布斯雜誌2月份給SpaceX算了一筆帳，到2025年，其天基互聯網年收入預計將達到100億美元。<br />\n<br />\n  文中估計，到2021年，星鏈計劃將獲得大約0.1% 的新增互聯網用戶，隨著覆蓋範圍的擴大，這個數字到2025年將上升到2.3%。新用戶將從2021年的20萬增加到2025年的560萬，估計到2025年星鏈的用戶總數約為1440萬。<br />\n<img src=\"https://nimg.ws.126.net/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fdingyue.ws.126.net%2F2021%2F0113%2Fb1e122b5j00qmvm4e0019c000hs008pm.jpg&amp;thumbnail=650x2147483647&amp;quality=80&amp;type=jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnimg.ws.126.net%2F%3Furl%3Dhttp%253A%252F%252Fdingyue.ws.126.net%252F2021%252F0113%252Fb1e122b5j00qmvm4e0019c000hs008pm.jpg%26thumbnail%3D650x2147483647%26quality%3D80%26type%3Djpg&h=372f1243&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n  而SpaceX內部2017年對收入和用戶的估計，該服務的每月用戶平均收入將達到60美元。這樣計算到2025年年收入將達到100億美元。<br />\n<img src=\"https://nimg.ws.126.net/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fdingyue.ws.126.net%2F2021%2F0113%2Fcf0de25cj00qmvm4e001oc000hs00b9m.jpg&amp;thumbnail=650x2147483647&amp;quality=80&amp;type=jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnimg.ws.126.net%2F%3Furl%3Dhttp%253A%252F%252Fdingyue.ws.126.net%252F2021%252F0113%252Fcf0de25cj00qmvm4e001oc000hs00b9m.jpg%26thumbnail%3D650x2147483647%26quality%3D80%26type%3Djpg&h=d50020b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n  星鏈優勢：<br />\n<br />\n  1、全球組網較5G地面基站組網，成本更低。（計劃上）<br />\n<br />\n  2、覆蓋無死角。（理論上）<br />\n<br />\n  3、信號強度超過5G。（計劃上）<br />\n<br />\n  星鏈劣勢：<br />\n<br />\n  1、製造更多太空垃圾。<br />\n<br />\n  2、前期主要用戶為5G無法覆蓋的偏遠地區。<br />\n<br />\n  3、衛星通信的頻段與WIFI信號不在一個頻段，不能手機直連。"},{"pid":"9d8f7e1b3b7c8ec96f2761f381beb32e44e615e2","tid":2368063,"uid":6981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T00:48:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d98a1396f9fb43541f194b3a74ce8bbb5b1db93c","tid":2368063,"uid":335434,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T00:49:55.000Z","msg":"Starlink覆蓋到全球之後網絡長城比萬里長城更有資格成為歷史文物<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba12f67fd569b8d995b7b6b0cd15dd52c6ae1b47","tid":2368063,"uid":4942,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T00:52:43.000Z","msg":"戴森球  @@"},{"pid":"7b337271639a51d01f9dd8491c5819af5e6cedd4","tid":2368063,"uid":35205,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T00:53:58.000Z","msg":"本來5G就係呃鳩人"},{"pid":"41b911aeb271524d3a3923fba0abb75442d02ec0","tid":2368063,"uid":244034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d98a1396f9fb43541f194b3a74ce8bbb5b1db93c","tid":2368063,"uid":335434,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T00:49:55.000Z","msg":"Starlink覆蓋到全球之後網絡長城比萬里長城更有資格成為歷史文物<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T00:58:51.000Z","msg":"但同時有班癲狗出嚟咬人"},{"pid":"148a8d4a9129c8a65e78623cb3859ad2f31cb3e5","tid":2368063,"uid":132898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T01:00:12.000Z","msg":"勁到呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f9a1210497e5ea19dfadf57e6efbfe6833514da","tid":2368063,"uid":84275,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"d98a1396f9fb43541f194b3a74ce8bbb5b1db93c","tid":2368063,"uid":335434,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T00:49:55.000Z","msg":"Starlink覆蓋到全球之後網絡長城比萬里長城更有資格成為歷史文物<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T01:08:22.000Z","msg":"大陸講明佢夠膽提供服務比大陸就會射落黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nElon musk都講左唔會係大陸提供服務"},{"pid":"2e735162ab7f1747f1a008927359a3abb1f7ede0","tid":2368063,"uid":84275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4f9a1210497e5ea19dfadf57e6efbfe6833514da","tid":2368063,"uid":84275,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"d98a1396f9fb43541f194b3a74ce8bbb5b1db93c","tid":2368063,"uid":335434,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T00:49:55.000Z","msg":"Starlink覆蓋到全球之後網絡長城比萬里長城更有資格成為歷史文物<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T01:08:22.000Z","msg":"大陸講明佢夠膽提供服務比大陸就會射落黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nElon musk都講左唔會係大陸提供服務"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T01:10:13.000Z","msg":"From BBC<br />\n<br />\n馬斯克擔心衛星被中國打下來<br />\n微博用戶「不高不富不帥在江湖」則問，「中國會不會把能覆蓋國土的WiFi衛星都打下來」。<br />\n看似戲言卻恰恰馬斯克所擔心的。<br />\n在2015年1月的一次活動中，馬斯克提及了中國的網絡審查給這項計劃在中國落地帶來的困難。<br />\n馬斯克稱，「我希望我們能夠與不同的國家達成協議允許其國民接入，但是這是需要一個國家一個國家談的。」<br />\n如果SpaceX不顧中國的規定，利用這些衛星為中國網民提供未經審查的網絡接入服務，會怎樣？<br />\n「如果他們對我們的做法不滿，他們會打掉我們的衛星，這就不太妙了。」馬斯克稱，「中國能做到這一點。所以大概我們不該在那兒提供服務。」<br />\n2007年，中國成功試射了反衛星導彈，一枚開拓者一號火箭攜帶動能彈頭，擊毀了軌道高度865公里的一顆已報廢的氣象衛星「風雲一號C」。其後又多次試射了具備擊落中高軌道衛星能力的導彈。"},{"pid":"b37c5a1bc37ddacbb739792c3c8407c6797e8942","tid":2368063,"uid":20241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d98a1396f9fb43541f194b3a74ce8bbb5b1db93c","tid":2368063,"uid":335434,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T00:49:55.000Z","msg":"Starlink覆蓋到全球之後網絡長城比萬里長城更有資格成為歷史文物<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T01:31:45.000Z","msg":"咪傻，你點比錢？信用卡一過數就有人上門啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86a5b8ba46ec2aa8bb7a13e678e4382a72dda966","tid":2368063,"uid":20241,"like":11,"dislike":3,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"4f9a1210497e5ea19dfadf57e6efbfe6833514da","tid":2368063,"uid":84275,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"d98a1396f9fb43541f194b3a74ce8bbb5b1db93c","tid":2368063,"uid":335434,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-01