slike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ba12f67fd569b8d995b7b6b0cd15dd52c6ae1b47","tid":2368063,"uid":4942,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T00:52:43.000Z","msg":"戴森球  @@"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T03:33:21.000Z","msg":"我都係諗到呢樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f5693007bbe0c0395551abc88ceebf554ab21e0","tid":2368063,"uid":41317,"like":1,"dislike":10,"score":-9,"citedBy":8,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T03:49:19.000Z","msg":"電動車自動導航喱啲新型業務我覺得ok<br />\n甚至所謂太空旅行我都由你<br />\n<br />\n但係starlink真係製造垃圾<br />\n萬一又有革命性傳輸技術，除左換過晒啲衛星就冇其他升級方案<br />\n冇網絡覆蓋嘅地方基本上就係窮鬼地方<br />\n嗰班人俾得起幾多錢養你個starlink<br />\n大城市又唔可能平得過固網寬頻/wifi<br />\n未計maintenance要幾錢<br />\n<br />\n純粹sell緊個big dream<br />\n如果elon musk有朝一日會破產，肯定就係衰喺starlink手上"},{"pid":"165308a83d8084659d1a42300a5ddd3bcfb9885f","tid":2368063,"uid":25345,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5f5693007bbe0c0395551abc88ceebf554ab21e0","tid":2368063,"uid":41317,"like":1,"dislike":10,"score":-9,"citedBy":8,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T03:49:19.000Z","msg":"電動車自動導航喱啲新型業務我覺得ok<br />\n甚至所謂太空旅行我都由你<br />\n<br />\n但係starlink真係製造垃圾<br />\n萬一又有革命性傳輸技術，除左換過晒啲衛星就冇其他升級方案<br />\n冇網絡覆蓋嘅地方基本上就係窮鬼地方<br />\n嗰班人俾得起幾多錢養你個starlink<br />\n大城市又唔可能平得過固網寬頻/wifi<br />\n未計maintenance要幾錢<br />\n<br />\n純粹sell緊個big dream<br />\n如果elon musk有朝一日會破產，肯定就係衰喺starlink手上"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T04:16:41.000Z","msg":"有限公司點會令個人破產<br />\n最多咪執左佢"},{"pid":"81dd1999dad7547c4d993b3e25acebabfbafcd03","tid":2368063,"uid":113000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T04:17:40.000Z","msg":"5g由頭到尾都係吹大左"},{"pid":"0c7c069969285e7a206fbf7a6c50a5040842aab0","tid":2368063,"uid":66087,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T04:20:36.000Z","msg":"3、衛星通信的頻段與WIFI信號不在一個頻段，不能手機直連<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n手機用唔到有咩用 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"462a72ecd6409d61fac3f96e0c90d831d183d949","tid":2368063,"uid":82929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9bf792e4ad18fd2661036a403c9667b241da3f82","tid":2368063,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T00:36:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://nimg.ws.126.net/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fdingyue.ws.126.net%2F2021%2F0113%2F7a95c024j00qmvm4e000wc000hs00aom.jpg&amp;thumbnail=650x2147483647&amp;quality=80&amp;type=jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnimg.ws.126.net%2F%3Furl%3Dhttp%253A%252F%252Fdingyue.ws.126.net%252F2021%252F0113%252F7a95c024j00qmvm4e000wc000hs00aom.jpg%26thumbnail%3D650x2147483647%26quality%3D80%26type%3Djpg&h=dbcff470&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n  2015年1月，馬斯克宣布SpaceX計劃將約1.2萬顆通信衛星發射到軌道，其中1584顆將部署在地球上空550千米處的近地軌道，並從2020年開始工作。這一項目被命名為&ldquo;星鏈&rdquo;（Starlink）。但據有關文件顯示，該公司還準備再增加3萬顆，使衛星總量達到約4.2萬顆。<br />\n<br />\n  <br />\n<br />\n  每顆225Kg一輛汽車大小。星鏈計劃有望覆蓋地球上所有難以涉足地方。<br />\n<br />\n  4月23日，SpaceX成功發射第七批60顆Starlink衛星，馬斯克發推特說，星鏈內測差不多三個月後開始，公測六個月以後。<br />\n<br />\n  <img src=\"https://nimg.ws.126.net/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fdingyue.ws.126.net%2F2021%2F0113%2Fae664129j00qmvm4e000rc000hs00a0m.jpg&amp;thumbnail=650x2147483647&amp;quality=80&amp;type=jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnimg.ws.126.net%2F%3Furl%3Dhttp%253A%252F%252Fdingyue.ws.126.net%252F2021%252F0113%252Fae664129j00qmvm4e000rc000hs00a0m.jpg%26thumbnail%3D650x2147483647%26quality%3D80%26type%3Djpg&h=de016cf9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n  馬斯克補充說，最初的測試將適用於高緯度地區。星鏈服務最初將在2020年提供給加拿大和北美客戶，並在2021年進一步擴大服務範圍至世界其他地區。<br />\n<br />\n  其實這種衛星電話並不是馬斯克首創，當年摩托羅拉投資的銥星系統就這麼幹過，但錢燒沒了，最終也掛了，而SpaceX沒蹈銥星的覆轍，原因就在於其較成熟的火箭回收技術。而其競爭對手OneWeb疫情期間軟銀撤資而宣布破產，與此同時SpaceX卻新獲5億美金融資，說明成本因素是SpaceX仍舊受資本市場追捧的原因之一。<br />\n<br />\n  <img src=\"https://nimg.ws.126.net/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fdingyue.ws.126.net%2F2021%2F0113%2Ff86724b2j00qmvm4e000lc000du007gm.jpg&amp;thumbnail=650x2147483647&amp;quality=80&amp;type=jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnimg.ws.126.net%2F%3Furl%3Dhttp%253A%252F%252Fdingyue.ws.126.net%252F2021%252F0113%252Ff86724b2j00qmvm4e000lc000du007gm.jpg%26thumbnail%3D650x2147483647%26quality%3D80%26type%3Djpg&h=6520c839&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n  福布斯雜誌2月份給SpaceX算了一筆帳，到2025年，其天基互聯網年收入預計將達到100億美元。<br />\n<br />\n  文中估計，到2021年，星鏈計劃將獲得大約0.1% 的新增互聯網用戶，隨著覆蓋範圍的擴大，這個數字到2025年將上升到2.3%。新用戶將從2021年的20萬增加到2025年的560萬，估計到2025年星鏈的用戶總數約為1440萬。<br />\n<img src=\"https://nimg.ws.126.net/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fdingyue.ws.126.net%2F2021%2F0113%2Fb1e122b5j00qmvm4e0019c000hs008pm.jpg&amp;thumbnail=650x2147483647&amp;quality=80&amp;type=jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnimg.ws.126.net%2F%3Furl%3Dhttp%253A%252F%252Fdingyue.ws.126.net%252F2021%252F0113%252Fb1e122b5j00qmvm4e0019c000hs008pm.jpg%26thumbnail%3D650x2147483647%26quality%3D80%26type%3Djpg&h=372f1243&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n  而SpaceX內部2017年對收入和用戶的估計，該服務的每月用戶平均收入將達到60美元。這樣計算到2025年年收入將達到100億美元。<br />\n<img src=\"https://nimg.ws.126.net/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fdingyue.ws.126.net%2F2021%2F0113%2Fcf0de25cj00qmvm4e001oc000hs00b9m.jpg&amp;thumbnail=650x2147483647&amp;quality=80&amp;type=jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnimg.ws.126.net%2F%3Furl%3Dhttp%253A%252F%252Fdingyue.ws.126.net%252F2021%252F0113%252Fcf0de25cj00qmvm4e001oc000hs00b9m.jpg%26thumbnail%3D650x2147483647%26quality%3D80%26type%3Djpg&h=d50020b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n  星鏈優勢：<br />\n<br />\n  1、全球組網較5G地面基站組網，成本更低。（計劃上）<br />\n<br />\n  2、覆蓋無死角。（理論上）<br />\n<br />\n  3、信號強度超過5G。（計劃上）<br />\n<br />\n  星鏈劣勢：<br />\n<br />\n  1、製造更多太空垃圾。<br />\n<br />\n  2、前期主要用戶為5G無法覆蓋的偏遠地區。<br />\n<br />\n  3、衛星通信的頻段與WIFI信號不在一個頻段，不能手機直連。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T04:37:36.000Z","msg":"等睇撞其他太空垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />變軌再變太空垃圾<br />\n<br />\n全個太空都變得唔安全<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c751268e38359630c9eadd678057921ee83180c5","tid":2368063,"uid":82929,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0c7c069969285e7a206fbf7a6c50a5040842aab0","tid":2368063,"uid":66087,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T04:20:36.000Z","msg":"3、衛星通信的頻段與WIFI信號不在一個頻段，不能手機直連<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n手機用唔到有咩用 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T04:39:23.000Z","msg":"偏遠地區、飛機、遠洋船用<br />\n<br />\n更平更快衛星通訊，唔洗吹到世界級發明"},{"pid":"056e45ea49b900e08f93f78f9988c325d6ee8099","tid":2368063,"uid":84275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"52ecb3235a3cd7060f4c9848ac5512bb1cd6f336","tid":2368063,"uid":20241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2f2d8627d827ec6b54c7ca6a578f91d9b1289dc2","tid":2368063,"uid":84275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"86a5b8ba46ec2aa8bb7a13e678e4382a72dda966","tid":2368063,"uid":20241,"like":11,"dislike":3,"score":8,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T01:39:47.000Z","msg":"你9up前知唔知要點用starlink<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n要買成set嘢，部接收雷達仲要擺出露台/天台<br />\n支共連入口都唔會俾你入到你點用<br />\n我懷疑好多人唔知starlink係寬頻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />個個以為佢係移動網絡"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T03:07:51.000Z","msg":"咪話大陸唔會比佢用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T03:23:32.000Z","msg":"你話佢俾大陸人用大陸會射佢落嚟<br />\n問題係你入唔到口設備點會有人用到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T04:55:03.000Z","msg":"Elon musk都咁講，唔係我咁講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />Elon musk講就唔係9up<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我複述就係我9up，你仲惡過共產黨<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n早在2015年1月，馬斯克（Musk）在西雅圖SpaceX工廠的活動中，就指出中國（中共）怎樣對他的計劃構成了重大障礙。他說：「如果他們對我們的做法不滿，他們會把我們的衛星炸毀，這就不太好了」，「中國（中共）能做到這一點。所以我們大概還不能在那兒提供服務。」[6]"},{"pid":"1f68b71c0e9a3d468da64d47757dfbd2625a04bc","tid":2368063,"uid":51121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T04:57:17.000Z","msg":"室內用到?"},{"pid":"ef00b012a8c24dd4c575471fc1676a4feb26f329","tid":2368063,"uid":125017,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"52ecb3235a3cd7060f4c9848ac5512bb1cd6f336","tid":2368063,"uid":20241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2f2d8627d827ec6b54c7ca6a578f91d9b1289dc2","tid":2368063,"uid":84275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"86a5b8ba46ec2aa8bb7a13e678e4382a72dda966","tid":2368063,"uid":20241,"like":11,"dislike":3,"score":8,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T01:39:47.000Z","msg":"你9up前知唔知要點用starlink<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n要買成set嘢，部接收雷達仲要擺出露台/天台<br />\n支共連入口都唔會俾你入到你點用<br />\n我懷疑好多人唔知starlink係寬頻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />個個以為佢係移動網絡"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T03:07:51.000Z","msg":"咪話大陸唔會比佢用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T03:23:32.000Z","msg":"你話佢俾大陸人用大陸會射佢落嚟<br />\n問題係你入唔到口設備點會有人用到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T05:01:26.000Z","msg":"一定有人偷運到入去架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44bebbf10c2744196ab8c6d2ad94436fba991e1d","tid":2368063,"uid":166095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4f9a1210497e5ea19dfadf57e6efbfe6833514da","tid":2368063,"uid":84275,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"d98a1396f9fb43541f194b3a74ce8bbb5b1db93c","tid":2368063,"uid":335